= Utilities =

Utility packages to use in API and Mods.

== How to use ==

<source lang="lua">require("CommunityAPI")

local StringUtils = CommunityAPI.Utils.String
StringUtils.SplitString("Hello world", " ")</source>
=== CommunityAPI.Utils.Inventory ===

<source lang="lua">FindAllItemInInventoryByTag(inventory, tag)</source>
